# --- Julia ---
*.jl.cov
*.jl.*.cov
*.jl.mem
/core/docs/build/
# Manifest.toml IS committed on purpose: this is an application/teaching repo,
# so a pinned, reproducible dependency set is a feature.

# --- Large simulation artifacts (regenerated by run_batch) ---
# Sweeps are ignored by default (the .meta.json sidecar travels with its .bin), EXCEPT
# the slice-1 ROC showcase below, which is committed (~3 KB) so the Pluto notebook
# renders on a fresh clone with no regen step. Other sweeps still won't be staged.
/shared/*.bin
/shared/*.meta.json
/shared/*.dat
/shared/*.npy
!/shared/roc_radar1.bin
!/shared/roc_radar1.meta.json

